<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">创客逐梦启新程 AI赋能向未来</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>第十九届校园文化艺术节</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">暨</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>第十届创客嘉年华</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">正式拉开帷幕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761813774698.png" alt="1761813774698.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761813774698.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>精心开场</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">看！在这个万众瞩目的时刻，我们以一场气势磅礴的“旗开得胜”，为本次嘉年华拉开最震撼的序幕！</span><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761813845487.png" alt="1761813845487.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761813845487.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>热闹表演</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">舞台光影流转</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">以歌舞诉初心,用表演承荣光</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">尽显山河与传承之韵!</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814027294.png" alt="1761814027294.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814027294.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">鼓舞《铁血军魂》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814273922.png" alt="1761814273922.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814273922.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">朗诵《五秩先锋诵》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814378950.png" alt="1761814378950.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814378950.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">古典舞《一条大河》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814448365.png" alt="1761814448365.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814448365.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">音乐剧《荣光里的回响》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">表演者怀揣热忱</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">用歌舞诠释青春</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">让活力与芳华尽情绽放!</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814913494.png" alt="1761814913494.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814913494.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">舞蹈《bangbang</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814966665.png" alt="1761814966665.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761814966665.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">走秀《荒境花叙》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815066513.png" alt="1761815066513.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815066513.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">街舞《燃青春》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815115385.png" alt="1761815115385.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815115385.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">服装展示《星芒集结》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">新征程的号角已经吹响</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">逐梦的脚步从未停歇</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">未来的篇章，等着我们书写辉煌！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815197278.png" alt="1761815197278.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815197278.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">乐队《火力全开》《烟火里的尘埃》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815274054.png" alt="1761815274054.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815274054.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">舞蹈《森林之子》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815329884.png" alt="1761815329884.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815329884.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">魔术《奇迹》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815374157.png" alt="1761815374157.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815374157.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">歌伴舞《乘风破浪再出发》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815417375.png" alt="1761815417375.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815417375.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px;">歌伴舞《向光而行》</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;"><strong>经管游行队伍</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">伴着轻快旋律，经管学院游行方阵缓缓登场。前方花车色彩明快，缀满象征经济与管理的创意元素；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;">两只憨态玩偶紧随其后，挥手致意惹得观众欢笑。后方队伍穿戴统一，步伐铿锵、动作协调，尽显经管学子的昂扬风貌与团队凝聚力，生动展现学院活力。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815579083.png" alt="1761815579083.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815579083.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815592039.png" alt="1761815592039.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815592039.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815604317.png" alt="1761815604317.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815604317.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815618525.png" alt="1761815618525.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815618525.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815629472.png" alt="1761815629472.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815629472.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815642799.png" alt="1761815642799.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815642799.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815655487.png" alt="1761815655487.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815655487.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815668331.png" alt="1761815668331.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815668331.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815678962.png" alt="1761815678962.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815678962.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815690399.png" alt="1761815690399.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815690399.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815701832.png" alt="1761815701832.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815701832.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><strong>谢幕</strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;">此次活动以“创客逐梦启新程，AI赋能向未来”为主题，既延续我校十届文艺与创客活动的青春基因，也注入人工智能时代的前沿活力。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;">这不仅为江西软件大学学子搭建了释放艺术才华、践行创客精神的舞台，也让经管学院学子在此轻松协作，共享创意成果、增进彼此认同，共赴这场星光熠熠的追梦之旅。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815772280.png" alt="1761815772280.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815772280.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><br></p>